metadata.name: Primitive Life 1
metadata.description:
Title: Primitive Life 1

Medium: Mushroom spores and juice on paper

Description: This piece was created using mushroom spores on watercolor paper. For three days the spores fell on the paper, and while they did, the mushroom hats began to rot and leak their juice. This  juice was then used to paint the watercolor-like portions of the primitive jellyfish.

Jacob Matthew Dix
